For $K=0$, $\underline{F}_K(M,K)=
{\left.\frac{\partial }{{\partial K}}\left( {K\underline {E\left[ R \right]} } \right)\right|_{K=0}\left( {\frac{P}{\eta } + MP_c  + P_0 } \right)}>0$. Combining Lemma \ref{lemmaconstraint}, we know that the solution for $\underline{F}_K(M,K)=0$ lies in $(0,u_{ASE}^*M)$ and can be obtained through the bisection method.
